borrow(bytes32,address,int256,int256).notice: borrow  deposit collateral and mint allETH

claimYield(bytes32,address,int256).notice: claim staking yield withdraw collateral amount equal to how much staking yield has accrued frontend just calls withdraw with specific amount they want to claim

deposit(bytes32,address,int256).notice: deposit deposit more collateral  same thing as borrow but with zero allETH minting  probably unnecessary

payback(bytes32,address,int256).notice: payback pay back borrowed allETH amounts

withdraw(bytes32,address,int256).notice: withdraw remove collateral from a vault shouldn't allow withdrawals past liquidation threshold
